history.content:
Please see the advice from the Scheduling Dept:

I recommend submitting a ServiceNow ticket and including screenshots of:

a) the classes in which the student is already enrolled,
b) the student's attempt to enroll in a conflicting class, including the error message received and all other data on the screen,
and 
c) their notification-less CalCentral dashboard.
If you send an email to sishelp@berkeley.edu, it will open a ticket.
history.subject: Conflict override form not appearing on CalCentral?
